[Nouns] uniformity; homogeneity, homogeneousness; consistency; connaturality, connaturalness; homology; accordance; conformity [more]; agreement [more]; consonance, uniformness.
regularity, constancy, even tenor, routine; monotony.
[Verbs] be uniform; accord with [more]; run through; become uniform; conform to [more].
render uniform, homogenize; assimilate, level, smooth, dress.
[Adjectives] uniform; homogeneous, homologous; of a piece, consistent, connatural; monotonous, even, invariable; regular, unchanged, undeviating, unvaried, unvarying.
[Adverbs] uniformly; uniformly with (conformably) [more]; in harmony with (agreeing) [more].
always, invariably, without exception, without fail, unfailingly, never otherwise; by clockwork.
